snippet.title: Undertale Wildfire - Intro Sequence
snippet.description:
Undertale Wildfire is a fangame following Riley, the human SOUL of Bravery. Get ready to experience a small vertical slice of Wildfire's revamped combat system this August 2024, with PLAYs and Trinkets and more! (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-5btStoPXLY)

Follow Undertale Wildfire on:
- Twitter: https://x.com/UndertaleWldfre
- Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/undertalew...
- Discord:  https://discord.com/invite/nAsmtPZ3w2

Slide art by Frigadae, 'Once Upon A Fearless Time' by evanjamesTM
